snippet.title: Killing Floor 2 Summer Sideshow event announcement
snippet.description: The Summer Sideshow starts this week with a new map, reskinned Zeds, and a bunch of new items. See more from the PC Gaming Show at http://www.pcgamer.com/watch-pc-gaming-show-2017-e3-livestream/.
